      "location": "woods",
      "text": "Today you are tasked with delivering a basket to your grandmother. She lives on the other end of the forest. The path is dark and crooked, you've braved it many times before, and today's forest is quiet. Too quiet. You feel the world hold its breath in anticipation.",
