    {
      "id": "A-BRANCH",
      "location": "camp",
      "text": "You wake up, shaking. In the dark, you see a pair of lights. They sparkle in between the trees, phasing in and out, growing larger and larger.\n\nYou hold the branch firmly and shout towards the lights. You wave it around wildly, making yourself as big and loud and intimidating as you can possibly be. In an instant, the lights disappear. You fall back down and huddle against a large tree. You won’t fall asleep tonight.",
      "image": "",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Next",
          "targetNodeId": "A-MORN1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A-MORN1",
      "location": "camp",
      "text": "The sunlight is harsh against your weary eyes, but makes you exhale deeply in relief. The night has passed.",
