      "location": "woods",
      "text": "",
      "image": "You tell the woodsman that you’re on a delivery trip yo your grandmother’s.\n\n“Oh, wait, I know you! You’re Red, right? Your grandmother mentioned you a couple of times.” He quiets, deep in thought. “But seriously. Look after yourself. Take plenty of breaks, and… It’s probably nothing, but there’s been more animals here lately. If they give you any trouble, try to be loud and swing something around. That should scare them off.”",
